## üõ† Building Wheels (for PyPI)

This project uses cibuildwheel to build platform-specific wheels.

GitHub Actions workflows:

.github/workflows/build_wheels.yml ‚Äî builds wheels for Windows/Linux/macOS.

.github/workflows/publish.yml ‚Äî publishes wheels to PyPI.

